  "title": "Design Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Develop and present innovative design concepts that balance functionality, aesthetics, and sustainability</li><li>Collaborate with the project management team to ensure seamless integration of the design process with overall project execution</li><li>Attend client meetings, presentations, and site visits as needed</li><li>Lead and manage the design process for a portfolio of architectural projects, collaborating closely with clients, project managers, and the design team</li><li>Oversee the production of detailed design drawings, specifications, and technical documentation</li><li>Ensure projects adhere to relevant building codes, regulations, and industry standards</li><li>Provide mentorship and guidance to junior designers, fostering their professional development</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
